{"lemma":"عُزْلَةُ","slug":"عُزْلَةُ","root":"ع.ز.ل","root_slug":"ع-ز-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ز-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28981","n28987"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B2%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"being alone"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"solitude, isolation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"detachment, reserve"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"aloofness, retreat, hermitage"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hamlet, thorp, village","tags":["Yemen"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"clan, tribe","tags":["Yemen"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a type of administrative division consisting of adjacent villages, translated as “sub-district” because below a نَاحِيَة (nāḥiya)","tags":["Yemen"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28981","headword_ar":"عَزَلَهُ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EazolN","text_ar":"عَزْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set it, apart, away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aside; removed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separated it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) i. e., a thing;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano gayorihi","text_ar":"عَنْ غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from another thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from other things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-  And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed, deposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"displaced, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, an agent, or a deputy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his office,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercise of authority."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazalahu","text_ar":"عَزَلَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani AlEamali","text_ar":"عَنِ العَمَلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed, deposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"displaced, him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the agency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"administration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"government"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ez~lhu","text_ar":"عزّلهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoziylN","text_ar":"تَعْزِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazalahu","text_ar":"عَزَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) [In like manner also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEzl","text_ar":"اعزل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said by Freytag to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Semovit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"En","text_ar":"عن"},{"kind":"text","text":", as on the authority of the K; in which I do not find it.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euzila","text_ar":"عُزِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, removed deposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"displaced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from his office, &c.,] (S, O, Msb,) used as quasi-pass. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazalahu","text_ar":"عَزَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in which sense ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnEzl","text_ar":"انعزل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [said to be] not used, because in it [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazalahu","text_ar":"عَزَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] no labour, or exertion, is implied. (Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazala","text_ar":"عَزَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujaAmiE","text_ar":"مُجَامِع"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paulò ante emissionem,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penem suum"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraxit, et extra vulvam semen emisit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, * Msb, TA. *) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazala EanohaA","text_ar":"عَزَلَ عَنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) the pronoun referring to the man's female slave, (S, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EazolN","text_ar":"عَزْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, Mgh, O, TA,) [vaguely expl. as] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not desire her"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEotazalahaA","text_ar":"اِعْتَزَلَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the motive being that the woman might not conceive. (Az, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazila","text_ar":"عَزِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EazalN","text_ar":"عَزَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a horse)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had his tail inclining to one side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by habit, not naturally:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) when it inclines to the right side, the Arabs deem it unlucky. (Z, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EazalN","text_ar":"عَزَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA","Az","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n28987","headword_ar":"عُزْلَةٌ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. (S, Msb) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A going apart. away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aside; removal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separation of oneself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * L, Msb, * K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a withdrawing of oneself from association"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"communion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secession:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it seems to be sometimes used in a sense similar to that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEotikaAfN","text_ar":"اِعْتِكَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEuzolapu EibaAdapN","text_ar":"العُزْلَةُ عِبَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Retirement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"self-seclusion, is a mode of religious service"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, L, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}